data.description: Highly upgraded spacious end unit town home with attached 2 car garage features a large living room w/vaulted ceiling, lovely balcony, cozy fireplace and custom entertainment center. Gorgeous & remodeled kitchen w/quartz countertop, custom back splash & upgraded appliances including a new microwave. Remodeled bathrooms w/stunning shower in master w/dual custom sinks, faucets & quartz countertop. Custom sink, faucet, mirror & countertop in 2nd bath. Luxury vinyl and ceramic tile flooring throughout. Custom shutter. view on you tube.The Verandas at gated community of Escala Village with access to wonderful community amenities offers an end unit town home highly upgraded and ready for occupancy.  Custom paint, vinyl, tile, fixtures and upgrades.  11x10 additional room can easily be converted to the third bedroom. Epoxied garage floor and storage shelves.
